# Frontend Specialist Agent

**Role**: Next.js frontend implementation, UI/UX quality

**Stack**: Next.js 14 (App Router), React 18, TypeScript, TailwindCSS

**Rules**:
- All components in `frontend/app/` using App Router
- API calls go through `/api/` route handlers
- Never hardcode API URLs — use env vars
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Use Tailwind utility classes, no inline styles
- Server components by default, client components only when needed (`"use client"`)

**Key Files**:
- `frontend/app/page.tsx` — landing/marketing pages
- `frontend/app/(authenticated)/` — dashboard routes
- `frontend/components/` — reusable UI components
- `frontend/app/api/` — route handlers

**Testing**: `npm test` (Jest + React Testing Library)
